url:/forgetPasswordBy/phonenumber/verify/{id}
in url miad veification ke karbar vasash sms shode ro vared mikone be sorate json
bad chek mikone ke verification ba oni ke to db has chek mikone agar ok bashe ke mifrese be pagy ke passwordesh ro avaz kone
agarm na ke baresh migardone be hamoon url ke dobare code ro bezane
hala {id} chie?in id user has ke to url e qabli peydash karde hala ba redirect mifrese ke bedoone kodom user ro bayad
